data.description: GREENVILLE COUNTY, COUNTRY LIVING CLOSE TO THE MOUNTAINS, LESS THAN 20 FROM GREENVILLE DOWNTOWN AND 5 MIN FROM GREER DOWNTOWN...NO HOA...This home invites about a half an acre lot with an above ground pool.  Pool is covered and has been winterized.  This two story, one owner home, corner lot has 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths and a 1/2 bath.  Walk in the foyer and you'll find the front living room followed by a dining room, a beautiful kitchen with lots of cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances including a gas stove, and a new dishwasher.  LVP Flooring throughout the first floor. Cozy up in the den while enjoying the gas fireplace that leads to a level, private, fenced in yard.  Outdoor features includes a pool, extended patio, full covered gazebo with lighting, a 2-car detached garage with heating/cooling, a separate new storage building with electricity that could also be used as a "tiny home".  The second floor offers an owner's suite with a large walk-in closet. The owner's bathroom features dual sinks, separate shower and a separate garden tub.  You'll also find 3 additional spacious sized bedrooms, full bath, and a Bonus room which can be used as an office or an additional walk-in closet.  The laundry room is also upstairs and convenient to the bedrooms. This turn key home is located just a few miles from Downtown Greer & minutes away from GSP Airport/I-85 for a quick commute.  Pergola and shed conveys with the sale of the house.  HVAC and Septic was last serviced and inspected in June 2023.  Schedule an appointment TODAY!
